  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You gather frigid wind into a single, concentrated point and violently release it in a straight line, instantly blasting those in its path with frost and ice. Creatures in the area take 4d8 cold damage. Casting this spell with 3 actions instead of 2 will cause a surface close to the blast directly beneath it to be covered in rime, making it difficult terrain for 2d4 rounds.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Critical Success</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> The creature is unaffected.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Success</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> The creature takes half damage and is slowed 1 for 1 round.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Failure</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> The creature takes full damage and is slowed 1 for 3 rounds.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Critical Failure </span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">The creature takes double damage and is slowed 1 for 1 minute.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:.5in\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Heightened(6<sup>th</sup>)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> The damage increases to 6d8, and when you cast the spell with 3 actions, the rime left behind expands to a 15-foot wide line.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Heightened(8<sup>th</sup>) </span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">The damage increases to 8d8, and when you cast the spell with 3 actions, the rime left behind expands to a 15-foot wide line lasting 1 minute.</span></p>"
